ChangeList.Description: The [Update printer](/graph/api/printer-update) method now supports application permissions and IPP encoding.

The following permission scopes have been added:
  • Printer.ReadWrite.All
  • PrintJob.ReadBasic.All
  • PrintJob.Read.All
  • PrintJob.ReadWriteBasic.All
  • PrintJob.ReadWrite.All
See the [permissions reference](/graph/permissions-reference#universal-print-permissions) for details.

Added the following resources to the Universal Print API:
  • [printTask](/graph/api/resources/printtask?view=graph-rest-beta)
  • [printTaskDefinition](/graph/api/resources/printtaskdefinition?view=graph-rest-beta)
  • [printTaskStatus](/graph/api/resources/printtaskstatus?view=graph-rest-beta)
  • [printTaskTrigger](/graph/api/resources/printtasktrigger?view=graph-rest-beta)
[Get printJob](/graph/api/printjob-get?view=graph-rest-beta) now supports application permissions, and **$expand=tasks**.
Added the [Redirect printJob](/graph/api/printjob-redirect?view=graph-rest-beta) method.
